{"tid":1239014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"612 口鼻吐血嗰個男仔","createTime":"2019-06-18T04:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T14:25:08.000Z","uid":155292,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b4054a6d7a67c3e7d3ac480ec3c6841635f1ee10","tid":1239014,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"其實有冇人覺得今次好奇怪？<br />\n<br />\n癌症伯伯，肚中槍<br />\n<br />\n女拔老師，眼中槍<br />\n<br />\n義士，太古廣場跳樓<br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅身份、背景、故事都係網上面廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n唯獨是有一幅圖，裏面口鼻吐血嗰個男仔，究竟係邊個？而家情況又點樣？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DScWuY1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDScWuY1.png&h=4dc903de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上個星期已經有人陰謀論諗係唔係醫館局(HA)封鎖消息。經過琴日陳議員爆料+HA回應呢件事，我已經對呢間機構冇晒信心。亦都唔再信佢哋上個禮拜話冇人死嘅聲明。<br />\n<br />\n其實如果HA有份封鎖消息都好簡單。萬一事後俾人踢爆左，佢哋要割嘅理由，只需要講一句話前線員工係個電腦系統到入漏咗 &ldquo;mass gatherings in legco&rdquo;，所以唔知道死者係同件事有關，就可以推得一乾二淨。<br />\n<br />\n依家好想大家幫手問吓有冇人真係識得佢，可以肯定佢安好冇事"},{"pid":"7877be7c43824575d9d1ff8247cba02990f7257d","tid":1239014,"uid":263522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"咁耐都冇消息 好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a883fff572444ecaee342e0729ae3ce6041c2190","tid":1239014,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有話佢ig出相話冇事出左院咩"},{"pid":"c488d5a8ee7dc9a86afd60c8aba9790e28c1f887","tid":1239014,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a883fff572444ecaee342e0729ae3ce6041c2190","tid":1239014,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:30:29.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有話佢ig出相話冇事出左院咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b91dc33b6f93ef80aaeef932ef65e3a1bbcef1","tid":1239014,"uid":69484,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:46:57.000Z","msg"